 \"the occasion\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with ET last month,KotbandGuthrierevealed that being away from their loved ones is the hardest part of their time in Paris covering the2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999858309822, \"rank\": 1.4169002744659943e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"ET\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"their loved ones\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest part\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"their time\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's so, so much fun.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much fun\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so beautiful.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so exciting that, of course, you wish that your kids were here.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"your kids\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You wish that your spouse was here,\\\" Guthrie, who shares Vale, 9, and Charley, 7, with her husband, Mike Feldman, said.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.211732390159716e-16, \"text\": \"Guthrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wood