tb\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"a valuable lesson\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's also teaching us that kids are fine when we are away for a few days.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are perfectly fine,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been FaceTiming our kids and communicating with them.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our kids\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes we feel like we have to be there all the time and [then] we realize they are growing, they are thriving, they are excited.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not wait to get home and see them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED CONTENT: Video News News News Streaming News\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RELATED CONTENT: Video News News News Streaming News\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3004}]}]}"